pageContext.claim: “The LameStream Media is the dominant force in trying to get me to keep our Country closed as long as possible in the hope that it will be detrimental to my election success. The real people want to get back to work ASAP.  We will be stronger than ever before!”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence that news organizations are pushing for businesses to remain closed because it would defeat Trump in the election; the recommendations are coming from Trump's own public-health advisers. Indeed, many news organizations are laying off staff or imposing furloughs because of a decline in advertising revenue.
